reviewText: Boston Blackie films were a gift for my wife. She loves these and is thankful that these shows are available today!
very good if you like older shows
These look bootlegged or they are recordings of recordings of bad recordings..  The image quality is the worst i have seen,

If you don't enjoy REMASTERED material this is your price point...I ordered several including Boston Blackie...and unless your familiar with
the story line or are a War baby the action/theme/plot is often difficult to follow...
